text:
After uploading the file use the response to get the file id and create a note engagement while attaching the file id to the hs_attachment_ids of the note. Sample request to the Engagement Note API endpoint below:

```{
  "properties": {
    "hs_timestamp": 1234567890,
    "hs_note_body": "Attachments",
    "hs_attachment_ids": [456123, 456789, 789132]
  },
  "associations": [
    {
      "types": [
        {
          "associationCategory": "HubSpot_DEFINED",
          "associationTypeId": 202
        }
      ],
      "to": { "id": 123456 }
    }
  ]
}```
